x, evolving environment of long\u2011haul flights. A and D have notable leadership or responsibility traits but lack any evidence of crew\u2011communication ability and have additional temperament or organizational issues.\n**Remaining uncertainties**\n1. Does Candidate\u202fB\u2019s weak numeric memory ever affect critical flight calculations or safety\u2011critical tasks?\n2. Do any of the other agents have any undocumented strengths in teamwork or communication for Candidates\u202fA,\u202fB, or\u202fD that could offset their current weaknesses?\nIf anyone can provide information on these points, it would help confirm whether B remains the best overall choice.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
